data.text:
Get a glimpse into the pre-show camaraderie in this exclusive video as Detroit dons Eminem and Jelly Roll link up before their explosive performance at the Michigan Central Station. In this behind-the-scenes moment, you can see the genuine respect between these hip hop heavyweights meeting before they unleash their energy on stage.

Eminem back on stage tonight in Detroit at the Michigan Central Station.

The pre-show starts at 8:00 PM EST, followed by the main concert at 8:30 PM EST, airing on YouTube and Peacock. Also, in the Detroit area, you can tune in to WDIV-TV Channel 4.
